				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: 2016 is the Year of VR
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1849184">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							Oh ,and before we get all super excited about all this new technology?<br />
<br />
It's important to remember that you're STILL told to disconnect your wireless and plug your device in with a LAN cable during many troubleshooting sessions with many companies and 802.11 has been around as a &quot;working&quot; technology since 1997.<br />
<br />
I'm all for VR being a thing, but the hype, unless it's somehow generating research dollars, needs to be stomped on.<br />
<br />
I want to see it become a fully functional reality, but I really truly despise it when people capitalize off of vaporware.
						</blockquote>
